    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the pros and cons, but some people say that with how fast the planet is warming, we dont really have the luxury of debating it anymore. like, if we dont go nuclear, we're basically doomed to miss all our climate targets. do you think that's a fair assessment or is that just being dramatic?",
